00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,000
‪[exhales]‬

214
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:37,920
‪[bass music]‬

215
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:46,360
‪[bass music]‬

216
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:47,960
‪[water splashes]‬

