about you.

1002
00:47:01,960 --> 00:47:03,440
-May I?
-Yes.

1003
00:47:04,000 --> 00:47:05,360
-Yes?
-Yes.

1004
00:47:13,920 --> 00:47:14,960
There we go.

1005
00:47:16,720 --> 00:47:19,800
-Yes, no, no, no, let people see it, yes.
-[laughs]

1006
00:47:19,880 --> 00:47:21,400
There we go, look at that.

1007
00:47:23,160 --> 00:47:25,040
I will cherish this every single day

1008
00:47:25,120 --> 00:47:26,560
for the rest of my life.

1009
00:47:28,520 --> 00:47:31,800
You should come over to my house.

1010
00:47:31,880 --> 00:47:34,000
We're having this
birthday party for my dad.

1011
00:47:34,080 --> 00:47:36,720
It's his 60th birthday,
so it’s like a big thing.

1012
00:47:36,800 --> 00:47:38,120
You should come as my guest.

1013
00:47:38,200 --> 00:47:42,160
