1015
00:47:45,520 --> 00:47:46,400
Do they know about me?

1016
00:47:46,480 --> 00:47:49,480
Oh, they'll find out when they meet you.

1017
00:47:49,560 --> 00:47:53,880
Look, I just want them
to meet you, you know?

1018
00:47:53,960 --> 00:47:55,520
Get to know you the way I have.

1019
00:47:57,000 --> 00:47:57,920
Come on, say "Yes".

1020
00:47:59,040 --> 00:47:59,880
Yes, I'll come.

1021
00:47:59,960 --> 00:48:01,520
