1025
00:48:14,080 --> 00:48:17,560
[gospel music]

1026
00:48:25,320 --> 00:48:27,680
[water running]

1027
00:48:27,760 --> 00:48:31,440
Oh wow, it all sounds so exciting.

1028
00:48:32,840 --> 00:48:33,720
Hmm-nnn

1029
00:48:34,320 --> 00:48:36,960
