1042
00:49:14,920 --> 00:49:19,240
And every time we bring it up,
he clams up.

1043
00:49:19,560 --> 00:49:23,040
Even Charlie has no
idea what his parents do.

1044
00:49:23,120 --> 00:49:24,840
