1049
00:49:34,720 --> 00:49:36,160
Now you are engaged.

1050
00:49:38,040 --> 00:49:40,640
Look, mum, I can't explain it, okay?

1051
00:49:40,720 --> 00:49:43,880
I just know. I can feel it, mum, I know.

1052
00:49:43,960 --> 00:49:45,480
He’s the one, mum.

1053
00:49:45,560 --> 00:49:46,640
Okay.

1054
00:49:46,720 --> 00:49:51,040
Well, call it a mother's intuition,

1055
00:49:52,640 --> 00:49:54,800
