1061
00:50:08,480 --> 00:50:09,320
All of them.

1062
00:50:11,480 --> 00:50:14,080
Okay, if you put it that way, honey.

1063
00:50:16,960 --> 00:50:18,920
Let's go.

1064
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:20,440
Okay.

1065
00:50:20,520 --> 00:50:22,400
Lola, I need you to style me.

1066
00:50:22,480 --> 00:50:23,440
