-Really?
-Hmmn

1076
00:50:45,320 --> 00:50:46,360
And who is it?

1077
00:50:46,960 --> 00:50:50,120
Do you remember Charlie's friend, Keme?

1078
00:50:50,200 --> 00:50:52,080
-The hot guy now.
-Ahnahn!

1079
00:50:52,160 --> 00:50:55,120
Oh my God. [laughs]

1080
00:50:55,200 --> 00:50:58,160
I do not
remember him because I haven't met him.

1081
00:50:58,240 --> 00:50:59,680
