1082
00:50:59,760 --> 00:51:01,440
I wish I'm coming with you.

1083
00:51:01,520 --> 00:51:02,360
No, please,

1084
00:51:02,440 --> 00:51:04,640
come and be going to
that your engagement party.

1085
