1095
00:51:27,560 --> 00:51:30,480
-Yes, this looks fantastic.
-Thank you.

1096
00:51:30,560 --> 00:51:34,160
[Keme] Listen, I invited
two friends over. I hope that’s okay.

1097
00:51:34,240 --> 00:51:36,520
