1113
00:52:19,920 --> 00:52:20,840
Mum, give me a break.

1114
00:52:20,920 --> 00:52:23,680
[Keme] When my friends come

1115
00:52:24,240 --> 00:52:26,480
You’ll get all the answers you need, okay?

1116
00:52:26,560 --> 00:52:27,920
But seriously, good job.

1117
00:52:28,400 --> 00:52:29,720
Thank you.

1118
00:52:29,800 --> 00:52:32,160
