1232
00:57:36,520 --> 00:57:40,240
Or else Ejike will
blow up and ruin everything.

1233
00:57:42,320 --> 00:57:43,680
How can I…?

1234
00:57:43,920 --> 00:57:45,920
Otunba is anxious to make a statement now.

1235
00:57:46,000 --> 00:57:48,880
Stall him, let me think about something.

1236
00:57:49,720 --> 00:57:50,960
[sighs]

1237
00:57:51,360 --> 00:57:52,400
Okay, hurry up, Nneka.

1238
00:57:52,480 --> 00:57:54,840
But I thought you said
you were working on him.

1239
00:57:54,920 --> 00:57:56,160
Yes, well, I am

1240
00:57:56,240 --> 00:57:58,240
I wasn’t expecting this girl.

1241
00:57:59,000 --> 00:58:02,240
Look, I promised to make
you president and I will.

1242
00:58:03,080 --> 00:58:05,440
I mean... we are so close now.

1243
00:58:05,520 --> 00:58:07,960
Nothing is going to stop us.

1244
00:58:12,320 --> 00:58:13,320
-[Charlie] This party seems cool
-Hey

1245
00:58:13,400 --> 00:58:14,920
Yeah, man. Thank you for coming.

1246
00:58:15,000 --> 00:58:17,240
Welcome to my little corner.

1247
00:58:17,320 --> 00:58:18,360
-Hey hey, please.
-Small.

1248
00:58:18,440 --> 00:58:20,520
Hey, please, we are a poor family

1249
00:58:20,600 --> 00:58:21,760
Keep saying that

1250
00:58:21,840 --> 00:58:23,240
At some point, you’ll
believe it. Keep saying that.

1251
00:58:23,320 --> 00:58:24,880
No, no, this is tiny.

1252
00:58:24,960 --> 00:58:27,560
-Kemi.
-[Kemi] Lola and Charlie.

1253
00:58:27,640 --> 00:58:28,760
Cuzzo.

1254
00:58:29,280 --> 00:58:30,600
-How are you?
-Hey.

1255
00:58:30,680 --> 00:58:32,240
What are you guys doing here?

1256
00:58:32,400 --> 00:58:35,200
-Is this the party you were invited to?
-Yes.

1257
00:58:35,280 --> 00:58:37,800
-Wait, this is your uncle's house?
-Yes.

1258
00:58:38,280 --> 00:58:41,720
-So he’s your--
-Ejike, my cousin.

1259
00:58:41,800 --> 00:58:43,800
Keme, Keme.

1260
00:58:44,120 --> 00:58:46,720
[Keme] Right, just one second.

1261
00:58:46,800 --> 00:58:48,280
How are you?

1262
00:58:48,360 --> 00:58:50,080
[Keme] I didn't know you were coming.

1263
00:58:50,360 --> 00:58:54,760
Yes, my full name is Ejikeme, Chukwuemeka.

1264
00:58:54,840 --> 00:58:57,080
I'll explain later.

1265
00:58:57,160 --> 00:58:58,880
Ok, you know what?
I don't know what's going on here,

1266
00:58:58,960 --> 00:59:01,840
but... wait a minute.

1267
00:59:01,920 --> 00:59:03,560
So Keme, if you're the only son,

1268
00:59:03,640 --> 00:59:04,600
then who exactly--

1269
00:59:04,680 --> 00:59:05,760
[Keme's dad] Uhhm

1270
00:59:06,360 --> 00:59:10,800
Thank you very much, friends and family,

1271
00:59:12,400 --> 00:59:16,120
Thank you so much for
coming to celebrate with me today.

1272
00:59:17,920 --> 00:59:22,560
I thank God for making me to see today.

1273
00:59:24,440 --> 00:59:28,040
-I am 60 years old, It’s not a joke.
-[guests clapping]

1274
00:59:29,160 --> 00:59:31,080
-[Keme's dad] My joy is double.
-[guests clapping]

1275
00:59:32,400 --> 00:59:36,520
When I received
a splendid news from my son,

1276
00:59:36,600 --> 00:59:40,480
Ejikeme, before this party.

1277
00:59:42,200 --> 00:59:44,800
It is with my utmost pleasure--

1278
00:59:44,880 --> 00:59:46,000
[Keme] Dad, please.

1279
00:59:46,080 --> 00:59:49,920
And joy to announce the engagement

1280
00:59:50,000 --> 00:59:53,800
of my only son, Ejikeme,

1281
00:59:54,600 --> 00:59:59,480
-to Wande Ayodeji
-[guests clapping]

1282
00:59:59,720 --> 01:00:04,280
the only daughter of
Otunba Ayodeji, thank you.

1283
01:00:05,400 --> 01:00:07,800
Thank you, thank you.

1284
01:00:12,600 --> 01:00:13,600
It's not what you think.

1285
01:00:13,680 --> 01:00:14,720
[Keme] Hold on, hold on, hold on

1286
01:00:14,800 --> 01:00:16,440
let me explain to you

1287
01:00:16,520 --> 01:00:18,240
-Let go, I’m fine,
-It's okay.

1288
01:00:18,320 --> 01:00:19,840
What is going on here?

1289
01:00:20,520 --> 01:00:22,360
Mum, not now, please.

1290
01:00:22,440 --> 01:00:24,200
Ejike, don't be rude.

1291
01:00:24,280 --> 01:00:26,920
Otunba wants to
understand what is going on here.

1292
01:00:27,000 --> 01:00:30,840
Mum, that's his problem not mine, okay?

1293
01:00:31,760 --> 01:00:34,880
Can you get this girl out of my house?

1294
01:00:34,960 --> 01:00:36,960
-Lola!
-Let's go, let's go talk

1295
01:00:37,040 --> 01:00:39,920
Lola, oya, come and be going.

1296
01:00:40,000 --> 01:00:41,320
Charlie, go and drop her.

1297
01:00:41,400 --> 01:00:42,880
She's... not going anywhere.

1298
01:00:42,960 --> 01:00:44,840
Ok, mum, she’s here on my invitation.

1299
01:00:44,920 --> 01:00:47,680
-So she gets to stay.
-Lola, for the first time in your life,

1300
01:00:47,760 --> 01:00:49,360
don't make this about you.

1301
01:00:49,440 --> 01:00:51,160
Don't come and
cause trouble in this family.

1302
01:00:51,720 --> 01:00:54,640
Lola, we know each other.

1303
01:00:55,680 --> 01:00:57,160
You better leave now before I expose you.

1304
01:00:57,240 --> 01:00:59,320
[Charlie] Expose her?

1305
01:00:59,560 --> 01:01:02,480
This is the girl
you knew since she was a baby.

1306
01:01:02,560 --> 01:01:05,280
[chuckles] You don’t know her!

1307
01:01:05,360 --> 01:01:08,720
I know exactly who she is,
thank you very much.

1308
01:01:09,520 --> 01:01:12,360
You don’t know who she is.

1309
01:01:12,440 --> 01:01:15,880
Her M.O is to take other people's men.

1310
01:01:16,680 --> 01:01:17,920
How dare you?

1311
01:01:18,680 --> 01:01:22,440
This is all a lie.
What did she do to you that is so bad

1312
01:01:22,520 --> 01:01:24,920
That you’ll say such
hurtful things about her?

1313
01:01:25,000 --> 01:01:26,120
Why not?

1314
01:01:26,200 --> 01:01:30,280
That's how she met
Femi for the first time.

1315
01:01:30,360 --> 01:01:32,720
-Ah.
-Eh, immediately.

1316
01:01:33,320 --> 01:01:38,120
Femi started running
after her day and night.

1317
01:01:38,200 --> 01:01:40,360
The most painful
part of this whole thing is

1318
01:01:40,440 --> 01:01:43,320
this girl did not even like the Femi,

1319
01:01:43,400 --> 01:01:47,960
but.. she just decided to ruin
Kemi's life.

1320
01:01:48,040 --> 01:01:50,280
Mum, what has gotten over you?

1321
01:01:50,360 --> 01:01:52,360
Femi was just a horrible guy.

1322
01:01:52,440 --> 01:01:54,520
Stop defending her.

1323
01:01:54,600 --> 01:01:57,080
For once in your life,
hold this girl responsible.

1324
01:01:58,840 --> 01:02:00,080
Hold her responsible
for what she did to you.

1325
01:02:01,080 --> 01:02:06,840
Ejike Chukwuemeka, this is
the girl you want to bring into my family?

1326
01:02:06,920 --> 01:02:08,400
This prostitute.

1327
01:02:08,480 --> 01:02:11,080
Ah!

1328
01:02:12,120 --> 01:02:13,280
Mum!

1329
01:02:15,400 --> 01:02:16,520
[iKeme] Lola, wait!

1330
01:02:16,600 --> 01:02:18,040
-Mum, why do you--
-[in Yoruba] Kinni?

1331
01:02:19,040 --> 01:02:21,880
[Keme] Lola, wait, wait.

1332
01:02:21,960 --> 01:02:24,280
Sorry, sorry. Please.

1333
01:02:24,360 --> 01:02:26,960
Look, Lola, just let me explain, okay?

1334
01:02:28,080 --> 01:02:30,440
I am sorry about that, you didn't
deserve to go through that.

1335
01:02:30,520 --> 01:02:33,080
[crying]

1336
01:02:33,400 --> 01:02:35,240
Why did you invite me here?

1337
01:02:35,880 --> 01:02:37,000
I wanted my parents to meet you.

1338
01:02:37,720 --> 01:02:39,520
Look, I meant it when I…

1339
01:02:39,600 --> 01:02:40,920
Lola, I love you.

1340
01:02:41,000 --> 01:02:43,200
-You lied to me.
-I didn't lie, okay?

1341
01:02:43,280 --> 01:02:45,440
Yes, I omitted the fact
that I am my father’s son, but

1342
01:02:45,520 --> 01:02:49,400
-it's not a lie.
-An omission... is still a lie.

1343
01:02:49,480 --> 01:02:50,720
I don't know who you are.

1344
01:02:50,800 --> 01:02:53,120
You told me that you are someone else,
I don't know you.

1345
01:02:53,200 --> 01:02:56,080
I'm the same guy you met... The same guy

1346
01:02:56,160 --> 01:02:57,280
What does it matter what my last name is?

1347
01:02:57,360 --> 01:02:58,360
Who are you?

1348
01:02:58,440 --> 01:02:59,720
Please, I don't know who you are.

1349
01:02:59,800 --> 01:03:01,640
Who are you? And who is Wande?

1350
01:03:01,720 --> 01:03:02,840
And what does
she have to do with all of this?

1351
01:03:02,920 --> 01:03:03,760
Okay, hold up.

1352
01:03:03,840 --> 01:03:05,680
The Wande thing, that's
just my mum being crazy.

1353
01:03:05,760 --> 01:03:06,600
I'll explain later,

1354
01:03:06,680 --> 01:03:10,160
but... you are the only person
I care about.

1355
01:03:12,800 --> 01:03:14,600
Lola, I'm the same guy.

1356
01:03:15,440 --> 01:03:16,680
Ok, the same guy
that fell in love with you,

1357
01:03:16,760 --> 01:03:19,040
literally seconds after meeting you.

1358
01:03:22,560 --> 01:03:26,520
I am the same guy who’s
standing here asking you, begging you.

1359
01:03:29,120 --> 01:03:31,840
Forgive me... Please.

1360
01:03:33,000 --> 01:03:33,840
‪[exhales]‬

1361
01:03:37,400 --> 01:03:39,680
I need some... space.

1362
01:03:41,160 --> 01:03:43,560
Look, I need to understand
what's going on,

1363
01:03:43,640 --> 01:03:45,480
I don’t understand, I'm confused.

1364
01:03:45,560 --> 01:03:47,280
Look, I need some space, please.

1365
01:03:48,000 --> 01:03:48,840
‪[sniffs]‬

1366
01:03:49,880 --> 01:03:51,800
OK. Fine.

1367
01:03:53,640 --> 01:03:55,160
I'll give you space.

1368
01:03:55,920 --> 01:03:59,040
But I meant it when I said I loved you.

1369
01:04:01,040 --> 01:04:03,040
So, don't expect too much space.

1370
01:04:05,160 --> 01:04:07,120
I’m gonna go get Charlie to take you home.

1371
01:04:12,240 --> 01:04:13,480
I'm never giving up on us, Lola.

1372
01:04:16,400 --> 01:04:17,280
Never.

1373
01:04:20,040 --> 01:04:21,280
I'll be right back.

1374
01:04:22,960 --> 01:04:23,800
‪[footsteps]‬

1375
01:04:27,160 --> 01:04:30,240
[sighs]

1376
01:04:32,120 --> 01:04:34,920
What is the meaning of this,
Ejikeme or Keme,

1377
01:04:35,000 --> 01:04:36,400
or whatever your name actually is?

1378
01:04:36,480 --> 01:04:39,760
Bro, it's still me, okay?
I wasn’t trying to lie to anyone.

1379
01:04:39,840 --> 01:04:43,120
It's just that I don't like
announcing he's my father, that's all.

1380
01:04:43,200 --> 01:04:46,240
I was trying to distance myself
from my parents' name, that's it.

1381
01:04:46,320 --> 01:04:47,600
That’s all well and good but

1382
01:04:49,080 --> 01:04:51,160
all I care about right now, is my sister.

1383
01:04:52,240 --> 01:04:53,120
You told me you loved her.

1384
01:04:54,120 --> 01:04:57,240
Are you serious?
I mean that more than you’ll ever know.

1385
01:04:57,320 --> 01:04:58,760
And I do intend to marry her.

1386
01:04:59,320 --> 01:05:00,960
So why then are your parents announcing

1387
01:05:01,040 --> 01:05:02,040
your engagement to this person?

1388
01:05:02,120 --> 01:05:02,960
Who is she?

1389
01:05:03,040 --> 01:05:05,040
And what's going on here, Keme?

1390
01:05:05,120 --> 01:05:06,840
I have no idea what
happened back there, okay?

1391
01:05:06,920 --> 01:05:08,360
I was completely blindsided.

1392
01:05:08,440 --> 01:05:10,640
[sucks teeth] This is like the…
what… second time I’m meeting that girl.

1393
01:05:10,720 --> 01:05:12,520
I don't even know her like that.

1394
01:05:12,600 --> 01:05:13,920
I'm not going to marry her.

1395
01:05:14,000 --> 01:05:16,080
Well, Kemi says that the whole
family has known about this for months.

1396
01:05:16,160 --> 01:05:18,840
Why would your own family do this to you?

1397
01:05:18,920 --> 01:05:22,160
Yes, my family is crazy. Okay?

1398
01:05:22,240 --> 01:05:25,480
I don’t know how else to explain it, okay?

1399
01:05:27,360 --> 01:05:30,680
Otunba Ayodeji has asked
my father to be his running mate,

1400
01:05:30,760 --> 01:05:33,680
four years down the line,
which I thought would be crazy.

1401
01:05:33,760 --> 01:05:36,680
But hey, my parents
want to lock down the position,

1402
01:05:36,760 --> 01:05:39,200
so they want me to
marry his only daughter,

1403
01:05:39,280 --> 01:05:40,840
which makes no sense.

1404
01:05:40,920 --> 01:05:42,400
But that’s just how they think, okay?

1405
01:05:42,480 --> 01:05:44,480
They told me about it,
I said: "No'' obviously.

1406
01:05:44,560 --> 01:05:48,200
but they didn't listen, so here we are.

1407
01:05:48,280 --> 01:05:49,960
Trust me, I had no
idea that was gonna happen.

1408
01:05:50,040 --> 01:05:51,120
I promise you.

1409
01:05:52,760 --> 01:05:53,760
They must not have heard me

1410
01:05:53,840 --> 01:05:58,560
or they just didn't care
because... now, there’s this.

1411
01:05:58,640 --> 01:06:02,000
Keme, this is a nightmare,

1412
01:06:02,080 --> 01:06:05,240
and my sister is
caught in the middle of it,

1413
01:06:06,280 --> 01:06:07,400
fix it.

1414
01:06:10,960 --> 01:06:13,560
I know, okay. And bro, I promise you,

1415
01:06:13,640 --> 01:06:16,400
I'll sort all of this, okay?

1416
01:06:16,480 --> 01:06:18,400
better sort it or you'll answer to me.

1417
01:06:20,800 --> 01:06:21,560
‪[footsteps]‬

1418
01:06:26,160 --> 01:06:27,440
‪[car door opens and closes]‬

1419
01:06:29,560 --> 01:06:30,200
‪[car ignition]‬

1420
01:06:47,400 --> 01:06:49,520
I am really sorry about the other night.

1421
01:06:49,600 --> 01:06:52,080
I had no idea you were
not aware of the arrangement.

1422
01:06:52,160 --> 01:06:54,200
For what it's worth,

1423
01:06:54,360 --> 01:06:56,200
I think she means well.

1424
01:06:57,000 --> 01:06:58,320
Yes, she wants people to think that.

1425
01:06:59,480 --> 01:07:01,520
Look, I have to ask you,

1426
01:07:01,600 --> 01:07:03,040
why are you going along with this?

1427
01:07:03,760 --> 01:07:05,160
I mean, come on, Wande, you are young,

1428
01:07:05,240 --> 01:07:07,720
you are accomplished,
you are really beautiful.

1429
01:07:07,800 --> 01:07:10,320
You don't need anyone
to set up a marriage for you.

1430
01:07:11,440 --> 01:07:14,320
This is what I’m groomed for, okay?

1431
01:07:15,160 --> 01:07:17,120
Besides, it's way easier this way,

1432
01:07:17,200 --> 01:07:18,840
'cos I know who I'm dealing with

1433
01:07:18,920 --> 01:07:21,400
and it is clear
you are not after dad's money.

1434
01:07:21,600 --> 01:07:23,360
Errr, fair enough.

1435
01:07:23,440 --> 01:07:25,920
Do you really think I'm beautiful?

1436
01:07:26,000 --> 01:07:29,360
[chuckles] Wande, I think you are a
lovely person,

1437
01:07:29,440 --> 01:07:32,240
I actually mean that.
You are really beautiful,

1438
01:07:32,320 --> 01:07:35,720
but... I fell in love with
someone already, okay?

1439
01:07:37,440 --> 01:07:39,640
And I actually intend to marry Lola.

1440
01:07:42,240 --> 01:07:43,520
[sighs deeply]

1441
01:07:43,600 --> 01:07:45,440
I am sad, honestly,

1442
01:07:45,520 --> 01:07:48,160
because I really think
we could be good together.

1443
01:07:48,880 --> 01:07:50,600
But it seems she’s a nice girl.

1444
01:07:50,680 --> 01:07:53,520
She is, she is, she is.

1445
01:07:54,600 --> 01:07:55,640
She is amazing.

1446
01:07:56,760 --> 01:07:58,160
[purse lips] Okay.

1447
01:08:01,160 --> 01:08:03,480
Look, I'm glad we had this talk.

1448
01:08:03,560 --> 01:08:04,680
-Me too.
-Okay.

1449
01:08:05,920 --> 01:08:07,000
I'm sorry things didn’t work out.

1450
01:08:07,080 --> 01:08:08,880
No hard feelings.

1451
01:08:09,080 --> 01:08:10,840
Thanks for being honest.

1452
01:08:11,240 --> 01:08:13,160
-Okay, no problem.
-Okay.

1453
01:08:13,400 --> 01:08:14,960
I’ll see you around?

1454
01:08:15,040 --> 01:08:15,840
-Yes, good
-OK.

1455
01:08:18,279 --> 01:08:19,840
‪[heels clicking]‬

1456
01:08:21,319 --> 01:08:22,160
‪[keyboard clicks]‬

1457
01:08:27,479 --> 01:08:28,800
[door closes]

1458
01:08:28,880 --> 01:08:29,800
Hi Mum.

1459
01:08:31,680 --> 01:08:33,319
How did it go?

1460
01:08:34,040 --> 01:08:34,920
How did what go?

1461
01:08:36,200 --> 01:08:37,319
How did you find Wande?

1462
01:08:39,200 --> 01:08:43,240
Uhhm, she's a nice person,

1463
01:08:43,640 --> 01:08:46,439
‪[keyboard clicks]‬

1464
01:08:52,479 --> 01:08:53,720
but she is not the one for me, alright?
Mum, I'm sorry.

1465
01:08:53,800 --> 01:08:56,399
But you just said she’s a nice person

1466
01:08:57,000 --> 01:08:58,920
What more do you want in a wife?

1467
01:08:59,200 --> 01:09:01,160
Mum, we’ve been over this.

1468
01:09:02,000 --> 01:09:03,600
Lola, is the one for me, okay?

1469
01:09:03,680 --> 01:09:06,800
Can we please not do this? Please?

1470
01:09:07,160 --> 01:09:12,279
I really want to know
what this Lola has given you?

1471
01:09:12,520 --> 01:09:14,920
What kind of juju has she given you?

1472
01:09:15,000 --> 01:09:16,720
I want to know her native doctor’s name.

1473
01:09:18,520 --> 01:09:20,680
[sighs] I'm not even gonna--

1474
01:09:20,760 --> 01:09:24,160
How can you let Wande go?

1475
01:09:28,160 --> 01:09:30,960
I mean she's tall

1476
01:09:31,040 --> 01:09:36,439
she's elegant,
she is so well mannered. She--

1477
01:09:38,600 --> 01:09:40,920
-Hmnn...
-Did you do this?

1478
